<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.github.H0lyDiv3r.croaqui</id>
  <name>Croaqui</name>
  <summary>A modern, lightweight music player for Linux</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Croaqui is a sleek desktop music player for Linux, built with Go and React. It provides powerful audio playback capabilities with support for multiple audio formats.</p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>High-quality audio playback using MPV</li>
      <li>Comprehensive playlist management</li>
      <li>Flexible queue system</li>
      <li>Full metadata reading and display</li>
      <li>Wide audio format support via FFmpeg</li>
      <li>Modern, responsive UI built with React</li>
      <li>Native Linux desktop integration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
